1
00:00:09,114 --> 00:00:13,160
♪I defy heaven, fate,
and so-called immortality♪

2
00:00:13,160 --> 00:00:17,800
♪At last you say
we've been apart too long♪

3
00:00:17,800 --> 00:00:22,840
♪Unwilling, unyielding, I won't let go♪

4
00:00:22,840 --> 00:00:28,000
♪With you, even a dried sea
learns to embrace a stream♪

5
00:00:28,000 --> 00:00:32,415
♪If heaven divides us, I'll reunite us,
with love as our vessel♪

6
00:00:32,415 --> 00:00:37,167
♪If it forbids it, I'll shatter
the absurd Heavenly Dao♪

7
00:00:37,167 --> 00:00:42,400
♪Even if countless stars
turn into my foes♪

8
00:00:42,400 --> 00:00:47,853
♪To grow old with you, we burn
through the end of the long night♪

9
00:00:50,820 --> 00:00:55,760
=Rise Again=

10
00:00:56,144 --> 00:00:58,878
=Episode 14=

11
00:00:59,479 --> 00:01:00,880
I don't want to go.

12
00:01:04,439 --> 00:01:06,719
I know you only love Ningxue.

13
00:01:07,280 --> 00:01:10,319
I just want to stay by your side.

14
00:01:11,040 --> 00:01:12,319
That's all I want.

15
00:01:17,680 --> 00:01:18,480
As long as you want,

16
00:01:19,680 --> 00:01:21,079
this will always be your home.

17
00:01:22,480 --> 00:01:23,000
Really?

18
00:01:24,120 --> 00:01:24,480
Yes.

19
00:01:42,799 --> 00:01:43,239
Keep warm.

20
00:01:52,120 --> 00:01:53,200
(As long as I'm with you,)

21
00:01:53,599 --> 00:01:54,719
(I don't care)

22
00:01:54,959 --> 00:01:55,879
(what my role is.)

23
00:01:57,040 --> 00:01:57,560
What?

24
00:01:57,840 --> 00:01:59,079
Why did you end up fighting him?

25
00:01:59,280 --> 00:02:00,359
I wasn't fighting him.

26
00:02:00,359 --> 00:02:01,719
I was avenging you.

27
00:02:02,280 --> 00:02:03,719
But his skills...

28
00:02:04,280 --> 00:02:05,400
are indeed pretty good.

29
00:02:06,840 --> 00:02:09,360
You're actually speaking up for him.

30
00:02:10,319 --> 00:02:12,879
Su Wubing has plenty of flaws,

31
00:02:13,039 --> 00:02:15,400
speaks all fancy, acts all superior...

32
00:02:15,759 --> 00:02:17,719
But yeah, the guy can fight.

33
00:02:18,080 --> 00:02:19,039
You should've seen it.

34
00:02:19,120 --> 00:02:20,879
Even my dad was impressed.

35
00:02:22,680 --> 00:02:25,080
Yingying, don't tell me you...

36
00:02:26,120 --> 00:02:26,680
What?

37
00:02:27,039 --> 00:02:28,879
I don't know what you're talking about.

38
00:02:30,080 --> 00:02:31,800
You've always been a bad liar.

39
00:02:32,719 --> 00:02:34,879
Fine, I admit he's strong.

40
00:02:34,879 --> 00:02:35,879
That's all.

41
00:02:37,479 --> 00:02:38,840
Relax. I'm just joking.

42
00:02:40,680 --> 00:02:42,639
(If Su Wubing joined the Shan family,)

43
00:02:42,840 --> 00:02:44,919
(then the two of us
would be unbeatable together.)

44
00:02:45,080 --> 00:02:46,680
(No one in Fan City could beat us.)

45
00:02:47,400 --> 00:02:48,039
Yingying.

46
00:02:48,759 --> 00:02:50,560
Don't tell me you've actually fallen
for him?

47
00:02:51,120 --> 00:02:52,080
How could that be?

48
00:02:53,000 --> 00:02:55,919
I just thought he looked cool

49
00:02:56,560 --> 00:02:57,680
taking down Gu Yuanbing.

50
00:02:58,759 --> 00:02:59,879
It has nothing to do with love.

51
00:03:00,479 --> 00:03:02,680
(I was mad about him
and Jiang Yao before.)

52
00:03:03,479 --> 00:03:04,759
(But if he did something wrong,)

53
00:03:05,039 --> 00:03:06,280
(Yingying won't let him off first.)

54
00:03:07,039 --> 00:03:09,039
(And I'm not going to beg.)

55
00:03:09,479 --> 00:03:10,840
(I just want some answers.)

56
00:03:13,000 --> 00:03:13,879
Where are you going?

57
00:03:14,479 --> 00:03:15,199
To find Su...

58
00:03:16,401 --> 00:03:17,381
(Dad)

59
00:03:21,520 --> 00:03:21,879
Dad.

60
00:03:24,159 --> 00:03:24,960
What?

61
00:03:25,680 --> 00:03:26,840
The Immortal Seeking Tournament?

62
00:03:34,840 --> 00:03:35,520
Get out!

63
00:03:35,599 --> 00:03:36,000
Yes.

64
00:03:36,039 --> 00:03:36,319
Get out!

65
00:03:41,280 --> 00:03:42,240
Mr. Gu.

66
00:03:42,719 --> 00:03:44,400
Why are you so angry?

67
00:03:45,560 --> 00:03:46,520
Didn't you say

68
00:03:46,879 --> 00:03:49,319
Su and Ningxue
were at each other's throats?

69
00:03:51,000 --> 00:03:52,639
Then why are they still together?

70
00:03:53,199 --> 00:03:54,120
Impossible!

71
00:03:54,120 --> 00:03:55,000
I clearly...

72
00:03:57,319 --> 00:03:58,599
Did you do something

73
00:03:58,599 --> 00:03:59,800
behind my back?

74
00:04:00,360 --> 00:04:02,240
No. Never.

75
00:04:02,360 --> 00:04:04,360
My heart is all yours.

76
00:04:08,639 --> 00:04:10,120
I suppose you wouldn't dare.

77
00:04:13,080 --> 00:04:13,879
Mr. Gu,

78
00:04:14,120 --> 00:04:15,639
since they're back together,

79
00:04:15,719 --> 00:04:16,800
should I try again...

80
00:04:16,959 --> 00:04:18,759
Do you think Su Wubing is stupid

81
00:04:18,759 --> 00:04:20,079
or Lin Ningxue is naive?

82
00:04:20,079 --> 00:04:21,600
They're definitely on guard now.

83
00:04:21,839 --> 00:04:22,560
Idiot.

84
00:04:36,160 --> 00:04:37,040
What is it?

85
00:04:38,800 --> 00:04:42,040
(Merciless Sword, Demon Clan)
You sent my junior Xue Wuhen

86
00:04:42,040 --> 00:04:44,199
after Su Wubing?

87
00:04:46,759 --> 00:04:48,079
I just asked him

88
00:04:48,079 --> 00:04:49,480
to teach Su Wubing a lesson.

89
00:04:50,040 --> 00:04:50,680
That's all.

90
00:04:50,680 --> 00:04:52,720
After I finish my seclusion,

91
00:04:52,920 --> 00:04:54,560
I'll handle him myself.

92
00:04:54,879 --> 00:04:55,639
Until then,

93
00:04:55,959 --> 00:04:58,319
just tell me where he is.

94
00:04:59,439 --> 00:05:00,560
Yes, senior.

95
00:05:00,879 --> 00:05:02,160
Please let go.

96
00:05:08,720 --> 00:05:09,519
Mr. Gu,

97
00:05:09,800 --> 00:05:10,720
what was that just now?

98
00:05:11,120 --> 00:05:12,199
So scary.

99
00:05:13,879 --> 00:05:14,560
Scared of what?

100
00:05:15,759 --> 00:05:17,079
This is a good thing.

101
00:05:17,639 --> 00:05:19,240
Xue Wuhen is useless,

102
00:05:19,879 --> 00:05:21,879
but his senior is strong.

103
00:05:22,680 --> 00:05:24,680
Su Wubing is dead for sure.

104
00:05:26,439 --> 00:05:27,240
Mr. Gu.

105
00:05:27,839 --> 00:05:28,240
Mr. Gu!

106
00:05:29,079 --> 00:05:30,399
Immortal Seeking Tournament is coming.

107
00:05:30,879 --> 00:05:32,319
Every family in Fan City will be there.

108
00:05:32,680 --> 00:05:33,879
Should we go?

109
00:05:34,759 --> 00:05:36,600
Yes. Definitely.

110
00:05:37,680 --> 00:05:39,279
The Lins will be there.

111
00:05:39,720 --> 00:05:41,279
So will Su Wubing.

112
00:05:42,160 --> 00:05:43,480
Perfect opportunity.

113
00:06:07,600 --> 00:06:09,600
(We never cleared things up last time.)

114
00:06:09,800 --> 00:06:12,160
(I don't know
if he'll even want to see me.)

115
00:06:24,000 --> 00:06:24,800
Follow me.

116
00:06:34,439 --> 00:06:35,040
Why did you come?

117
00:06:43,279 --> 00:06:44,199
Try it first.

118
00:07:08,279 --> 00:07:09,199
Ningxue.

119
00:07:10,680 --> 00:07:11,800
Why are you here?

120
00:07:13,040 --> 00:07:14,279
I came to see you.

121
00:07:15,560 --> 00:07:17,879
This place is so clean.

122
00:07:18,079 --> 00:07:18,879
You must have tidied up.

123
00:07:19,560 --> 00:07:20,160
Nice job.

124
00:07:21,160 --> 00:07:22,000
It's nothing.

125
00:07:22,279 --> 00:07:24,879
I just clean it now and then.

126
00:07:39,480 --> 00:07:40,040
Ningxue,

127
00:07:40,360 --> 00:07:41,600
did you come to see Wubing

128
00:07:41,959 --> 00:07:43,240
for something?

129
00:07:53,279 --> 00:07:56,279
(This outfit fits him perfectly.)

130
00:07:56,839 --> 00:07:58,079
(He looks so handsome.)

131
00:07:59,480 --> 00:08:00,000
Come with me.

132
00:08:01,480 --> 00:08:02,279
Where to?

133
00:08:03,160 --> 00:08:05,600
The Immortal Seeking Tournament
is about to start.

134
00:08:05,680 --> 00:08:06,680
Come with me.

135
00:08:07,680 --> 00:08:09,360
(She knows about that too.)

136
00:08:10,279 --> 00:08:11,279
(Let's see)

137
00:08:11,920 --> 00:08:14,759
(what level your cultivation is at.)

138
00:08:19,199 --> 00:08:19,600
Bye.

139
00:08:29,560 --> 00:08:30,079
Miss,

140
00:08:30,560 --> 00:08:31,519
the master said

141
00:08:32,039 --> 00:08:33,720
if you really don't want to go back,

142
00:08:34,039 --> 00:08:34,799
take the Su Wubing

143
00:08:35,559 --> 00:08:37,879
to the Immortal Seeking Tournament.

144
00:08:38,080 --> 00:08:38,759
First,

145
00:08:38,759 --> 00:08:40,080
he wants to see

146
00:08:40,080 --> 00:08:41,679
how the families
are positioning themselves.

147
00:08:42,080 --> 00:08:42,799
Second,

148
00:08:42,799 --> 00:08:43,679
he wants to know

149
00:08:43,679 --> 00:08:45,679
what Su Wubing is really capable of.

150
00:08:47,759 --> 00:08:49,600
Immortal Seeking Tournament...

151
00:09:16,059 --> 00:09:18,785
(Chen family, Zhong family,
Zhang family, Li family, Xue family)

152
00:09:42,720 --> 00:09:45,000
The Heavenly God Sword is there now.

153
00:09:45,639 --> 00:09:47,320
If you can make it

154
00:09:48,039 --> 00:09:49,240
to recognize you again,

155
00:09:49,840 --> 00:09:51,519
it might help you

156
00:09:51,519 --> 00:09:53,879
regain your Heavenly God Realm faster.

157
00:09:55,679 --> 00:09:57,320
(So Tianmiao wasn't wrong.)

158
00:09:58,039 --> 00:10:00,200
(I can already sense the aura
of the Sword.)

159
00:10:02,559 --> 00:10:03,759
Once we reach the gate,

160
00:10:04,080 --> 00:10:04,759
follow me.

161
00:10:05,399 --> 00:10:06,200
Keep quiet.

162
00:10:09,639 --> 00:10:10,080
Wait.

163
00:10:10,879 --> 00:10:12,000
At Two Realms Mountain,

164
00:10:12,240 --> 00:10:13,440
strength rules everything.

165
00:10:13,960 --> 00:10:15,080
Only the strongest

166
00:10:15,080 --> 00:10:16,559
walk through the middle.

167
00:10:17,039 --> 00:10:18,039
Everyone else

168
00:10:18,039 --> 00:10:19,639
enters from the sides?

169
00:10:20,559 --> 00:10:21,360
Su Wubing.

170
00:10:23,120 --> 00:10:24,600
If Wubing

171
00:10:24,720 --> 00:10:27,200
enters through the main gate,

172
00:10:27,480 --> 00:10:30,879
that would honor this place.

173
00:10:32,279 --> 00:10:32,840
Follow Ningxue.

174
00:10:33,360 --> 00:10:34,320
Low profile.

175
00:10:36,519 --> 00:10:37,519
Why are you here?

176
00:10:39,159 --> 00:10:40,080
Who is this?

177
00:10:41,080 --> 00:10:42,879
Miss Lin of the Lin family?

178
00:10:43,519 --> 00:10:44,720
The rumors don't do your justice.

179
00:10:45,240 --> 00:10:46,559
You're stunning.

180
00:10:47,200 --> 00:10:50,240
No wonder Su Wubing
is so hung up on you.

181
00:10:50,759 --> 00:10:51,559
Xiaonuan...

182
00:10:55,480 --> 00:10:56,639
Let me introduce myself.

183
00:10:57,240 --> 00:11:00,240
Su Wubing is my personal doctor.

184
00:11:01,240 --> 00:11:03,879
He treats me every week.

185
00:11:05,919 --> 00:11:06,720
Su Wubing!

186
00:11:10,039 --> 00:11:11,080
What took you so long?

187
00:11:11,080 --> 00:11:12,480
My father has been waiting for you.

188
00:11:16,399 --> 00:11:17,279
Wubing,

189
00:11:17,279 --> 00:11:18,480
you're really popular.

190
00:11:19,159 --> 00:11:19,759
Let's go up.

191
00:11:20,159 --> 00:11:21,879
The tournament is about to start.

192
00:11:22,799 --> 00:11:23,600
Why rush?

193
00:11:23,840 --> 00:11:24,879
You promised to help me

194
00:11:24,879 --> 00:11:26,120
find medicinal herbs.

195
00:11:26,639 --> 00:11:27,519
Did you?

196
00:11:27,639 --> 00:11:29,000
What herbs?

197
00:11:29,279 --> 00:11:31,120
Our martial hall
has plenty of good stuff.

198
00:11:31,279 --> 00:11:33,399
I'll have my junior
send you some.

199
00:11:34,799 --> 00:11:35,279
Su Wubing!

200
00:11:36,200 --> 00:11:36,720
Come with me.

201
00:11:41,480 --> 00:11:42,600
- Su Wubing!
- Su Wubing!

202
00:12:08,162 --> 00:12:12,265
♪I defy heaven, fate,
and so-called immortality♪

203
00:12:12,265 --> 00:12:16,985
♪At last you say
we've been apart too long♪

204
00:12:16,985 --> 00:12:21,865
♪Unwilling, unyielding, I won't let go♪

205
00:12:21,865 --> 00:12:26,985
♪With you, even a dried sea
learns to embrace a stream♪

206
00:12:26,985 --> 00:12:31,385
♪If heaven divides us, I'll reunite us,
with love as our vessel♪

207
00:12:31,385 --> 00:12:36,065
♪If it forbids it, I'll shatter
the absurd Heavenly Dao♪

208
00:12:36,065 --> 00:12:41,465
♪Even if countless stars
turn into my foes♪

209
00:12:41,465 --> 00:12:47,859
♪To grow old with you, we burn
through the end of the long night♪
